text:

Abhi toh ek saal aur hai saath...

text:
Bhai, Corrosion ka endsem cancel karwaya tumne, sabse acha kaam wahi kiya...
baaki toh 3 saal Profs ko galiyaana, assignment saath me karna aur kisi tarah course paas karna...yahi baaten yaad aayengi...
BHU me yaad hai humne kitni saari iitk me sporting culture ki problems discuss ki thi...hopefully tune kaam kiya hoga unpar...
All the best bhai for future...aise hi har jagah chaapte raho...

text:
Pandey ji,
Listening to your hundreds of startup ideas. Making insta pages(La_manquer) together. Saath me term paper likhna, presentation banana,  aur saath me Solar wale course me g**nd phatne take
yahi baaten yaad aayengi...
Aise hi mehnat karte raho, difficult situation me camly decisions lo jaise abhi lete ho, aur startup idea aaye toh call kariyo...
Gaandu courses niptane me saath dene k liye dhanyawaad...
Teri gaaliyan sunte sunte 4 saal nikal gaye aur teri gaaliyon ki wajah se hi maine yearbook banayi.

text:
Bhai tere bina kaise hi hote mere courses....har exam k pehle mai tere room pe aata tha poochne ki kitna hua tera aur tu hamesha bolta tha ki mujhe padha de ......prof ko saath me galiyana, labs me b bakchodi karna, paper k pehle randi rona karna...sab yaad rahega yaar...
tere saath court ki bench pe baaten karna, teri JEE k time wali kahaniyan sunte sunte 4 saal nikal gaye, mess me tere ghatia sawalon k jawab dene me bhi maja aaya kaafi, woh techkrii wali raat toh kabhi nhi bhool sakte yaar...kuch jyada hi bata diya tujhe maine tab...
lekin aakhir sem me jo courses saath kar rahe the woh dono drop kardiye tune harami...
Aise hi mast raho...Nischay ki gaand marte raho aur jeevan me chaapte raho...
kabhi bhi baat karni ho toh msg kardiyo bhai...
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
Bhai maje hi aagaye tere saath, lekin tu physics me bhaag gaya...Prof k baare me randirona karna, 2nd year me assignment saath me karna, tera antaragni ka randirona...intern k liye saath me apply karna...memorable tha..
tere saath mumbai ghoomna...tere ghar me 3 din me maja hi aagaya...aunty k haath ka khana mast tha yaar...
chinta mat kar achi phd uthayega tu....all the best bhai
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
Hota sir, apna scientific temper hamse bhi share kariye thoda...
Prof ko galiyana, supervisors ki burai karna aur pichle saal PhD k liye randi rona karna...
yahi same aadaten toh hame acha dost banati hain
Gaandu courses me saath dene k liye dhanyawaad...
Budding biologist cum materials scientist...chinta mat kar achi jagah PhD milegi tumhe
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
Bhai yaad hai first time kaise mile the?...L20 me saath me baithkar Prof ko galiya rahe the aur maine randomly pooch liya ki kaha se ho....phir toh city, coaching sab same...aur hum dost ban gaye...
first year me NCL me raat me saath me padhna, randirona karna first year kaise hi nikal gaya pta hi nhi chala...
Phir tumhare ghar aakar woh unacademy wala video banaya...memorable aur funny tha...
Ab toh dual bhi saath me hi hai...college me hopefully milenge aur bakchodi karenge...
All the best bro....kabhi bhi msg/call karliyo....
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
First time toh summer camp me dekha tha...jab hum apna wooden court wapas lene aaye the. Tumse as such toh jyada baat nhi hui...but train journey me first time baat hui (mai kuch khaas toh bola nhi), aur mujhe yaad hai ID card mangwake phir dekha tak nhi tha tumne.... lekin jab baad me cards khele the tab baat hui thi ache se...thats a nice memory.
Phir ESC201 ka quiz saath me diya tha....poora comedy tha...
You were always a good sport...ache se baat ki tumne hamesha expect for that proposal...
All the best for future...aise hi mast raho...

text:
Bhai summer camp me tumhare cooler ki wajah se  maine apne room mates ko chodda  tha, aaj bhi taane dete hain woh log....bahut maja aaya yaar tumhare saath summer camp me khelkar, ice packets lekar Shin Pain ka randi rona karna, ma'am ki burayi karna...sab memorable tha....
Yaar aur khelna chahiya tha  basketball tumhe....bahut maja aata...
Rebound k liye choten khana saath me, aur humara failed Goa plan banana....
All the best  bhai...aise hi mast raho aur jokes
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
Dubble bhai....tumhara 'dhawal sho't pe rebound lena aaj bhi yaad hai mujhe...yaar tumne toh basketball beech me  hi chodd diya...
lekin summer camp me jo masti kari thi woh sab tumhare jokes ki wajah se hi thi...ma'am ki mimicking karna...lakdi wala board hota toh jaroor jaata...bahut maja aaya bhai...
Aur jab apan log SG bane the tab bhi bahut masti kiye the...
All the best bhai...aise hi jokes maarte raho, songs likhte raho...
kabhi basketball khelte hain bhai milo toh...
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
Bhai summer camp me kya maje aaye the....tera har roj subah der tak socks pehenna....ice pack lagakar Shin Pain ka randirona karna, tere saath plays ki practice karna, one-on-one khelna, gym kayi baar saath me karna....udghosh me saath khelna...bhai maje hi aagaye...
Tere se achi feed kisine nhi ki mujhe court pe ( just kidding)... feeder ki aankhen chaaron taraf rehni chahiye, lakdi ka board hota toh jaroora jaati andar....maam ki burayi karna was memorable...kabhi saath me baithe toh wapas karenge
Tujhe aur khelna chahiye tha yaar....maza hi aa jati yaar saath khelte toh...kabhi mile toh wapas one-on-one khelenge...
Last me 2 course saath me bhi kar liye...aur dono me A...
Milte hain kabhi kisi court pe dost....
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh

text:
Mai 'KHUSH' search kar rha tha tabse toh koi result hi nhi aa raha tha isliye late ho gaya memoir likhne me.

Masti masti me degree bhi khatm ho gayi teri. Tu jab sota tha toh mai jagta tha aur jab tu sota toh mai jagta...isliye kuch khaas toh hai nhi boolne ko (waise tujhe yaad hai na jab tu so raha  tha ekbar toh teri poori pant khisak gayi thi?...aage nhi boloonga kuch)

Aise hi mast raho...Baaki toh apan baat karte hi rehte hain....kabhi bhi gaali khane ka mann kare toh call karliyo...

Yaar shivam ne register nhi kiya warna itna gaali dene ka mann tha usse...

text:

bc tere saath jis course me bhi raha hoon woh sab bekar hue hain mere...chahe Economics wala ho ya Solar wala....lekin maza bahut aayi bhai tere saath, tera randi rona kabhi nhi bhool sakta...

text:
Corssover Saxena bhai!! 
Summer camp me pehli baar mulakat hui ache se, aur bhai tumne bahut ache se summer camp conduct karwaya. Tumne wooden court ka arrangement karwa k meri dream poori kardi bhai. Maine toh summers k baad bhi continue kiya lekin summer camp jaisa maza phir kabhi bhi nhi aaya....tumko continue karna chahiye  tha, aur crossover dekhne ko milte...saath ragging lete baccho ki...bc raaj karte apan.

Humne toh udghosh bhi saath khela...woh GnS ki photo Rishabh har saal daalta rehta hai jisme dikh toh tum rahe ho lekin tag mujhe kiya hua hai...
Bhai phirse BB khelne ka bahut mann hai poori team k saath...
Milte hain phir kabhi kisi court pe...All the best

text:
Rishabh bhaiya,
summer camp me aapke 3 pointers aur woh acrobatic layups ko kabhi na bhool payenge, summer camp me itna maza aapke bina nhi ho sakta tha. Ma'am ki burai karna, gym saath me karna...aur udghosh me saath me khelna kaafi memorable tha...
Galaxy karwane k liye tumne basketball chodd diya tha..bahut bura laga yaar, saath me khelte inter iit jaate, juniors ki ragging lete maja hi aa jata...
kabhi saath me khelenge apan summer camp wale sablog...
All the best bhai....aise  hi mast raho, nayi cheezen karte raho aur tumhari next chess stream pe bhi first oppennt mai hi hoonga

text:
harami sale,

Ab toh saare profs ko milkar galiyana, assignment saath karna, labs me bakchodi karna...kisi tarah course paas karna...yahi yaaden hain..

text:
Suhail Khan!

text:
Bhai Kwade (tum branch opener aur mai branch closer),
ELS me saath me mile aur wahi se hi hamne randirona shuru kar diya tha kii itni late kyu roke hue hain, bahut  maja aaya tha hall 3 ko jeette hue dekhkar aur tumhari team k saath time spend karke...
Phir baad me toh ache dost ban hi gaye..profs ko galiyana, labs saath me ki, courses kisi tarah saath me niptaye...aur ab dual me bhi saath me hain...
campus khulne ki deri hai bakchodi karenge saath me...
All the best bhai...aise hi chaapte raho..

text:
Bajpai...
'Go to' person ho tum agar mujhe kabhi bhi koi information/help/advice chahiye hoti hai toh...
Tumne first year me kharrate le lekar itna tang kiya tha ki, maine tumhe kabhi bhi time se breakfast k liye nhi uthaya kabhi...
Tumhara seniors k saath 'interaction' pe rona, kd-rm jaana, woh PHY103 k endsem me saath me NCL me subah tak padhna...sab hamesha yaad rahega
first year me bhaalu jaise shareer se slim hone tak sab dekha hai bhai...
har midsem-endsem k pehle randirona karna, khush aur shivam ko gaaliyan dena...sab yaad rahega...
Tumse toh hamesha hi baat hoti rahegi...time khatam hone wala hai aur bahut kuch hai likhne ko...
All the best for future..
author: Ujjwal Pratap Singh
